[
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "However, the <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">war</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"0752\" class=\"\">prolonged</st> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">between</st> the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">and</st> the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>. <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> was <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">becoming</st> steadily <st data-num=\"02390\" class=\"\">stronger</st>, while the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> was <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">becoming</st> increasingly <st data-num=\"01800\" class=\"\">weaker</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Now <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> were <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">born</st> to <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> in <st data-num=\"02275\" class=\"\">Hebron</st>. His <st data-num=\"01060\" class=\"\">firstborn</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"0550\" class=\"\">Amnon</st>, born to <st data-num=\"0293\" class=\"\">Ahinoam</st> the <st data-num=\"03159\" class=\"\">Jezreelite</st>. ",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "His <st data-num=\"04932\" class=\"\">second</st> son<n id=\"1\" /> was <st data-num=\"03609\" class=\"\">Kileab</st>, born to <st data-num=\"026\" class=\"\">Abigail</st> the <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">widow</st><n id=\"2\" /> of <st data-num=\"05037\" class=\"\">Nabal</st> the <st data-num=\"03761\" class=\"\">Carmelite</st>. His <st data-num=\"07992\" class=\"\">third</st> son was <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"04601\" class=\"\">Maacah</st> <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughter</st> of <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"08526\" class=\"\">Talmai</st> of <st data-num=\"01650\" class=\"\">Geshur</st>. ",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "His <st data-num=\"07243\" class=\"\">fourth</st> son was <st data-num=\"0138\" class=\"\">Adonijah</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"02294\" class=\"\">Haggith</st>. His <st data-num=\"02549\" class=\"\">fifth</st> son was <st data-num=\"08203\" class=\"\">Shephatiah</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"037\" class=\"\">Abital</st>.",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "His <st data-num=\"08345\" class=\"\">sixth</st> son was <st data-num=\"03507\" class=\"\">Ithream</st>, born to <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wife</st> <st data-num=\"05698\" class=\"\">Eglah</st>. <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">These</st> sons<n id=\"1\" /> were all <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">born</st> to <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> in <st data-num=\"02275\" class=\"\">Hebron</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">As</st> the <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">war</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">continued</st> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">between</st> the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">and</st> the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">becoming more influential</st><n id=\"1\" /> in the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st>. ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "Now <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> had a <st data-num=\"06370\" class=\"\">concubine</st> <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">named</st> <st data-num=\"07532\" class=\"\">Rizpah</st> <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughter</st> of <st data-num=\"0345\" class=\"\">Aiah</st>. <st data-num=\"0378\">Ish Bosheth</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04069\" class=\"\">Why</st> did you <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">sleep</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">with</st><n id=\"2\" /> my <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"06370\" class=\"\">concubine</st>?\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">These</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">words</st> of <st data-num=\"0378\" class=\"\">Ish Bosheth</st> <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">really</st> <st data-num=\"02734\" class=\"\">angered</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> and he <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cAm <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> the <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st> of a <st data-num=\"03611\" class=\"\">dog</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> belongs to <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>? This very <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> I am <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">demonstrating</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"02617\" class=\"\">loyalty</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> your <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father</st> and <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> his <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">relatives</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">and</st> his <st data-num=\"04828\" class=\"\">friends</st>! I have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">betrayed</st> you into the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> of <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>. Yet you have <st data-num=\"06485 05921\">accused</st> me of <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">sinning</st> with this <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">woman</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">today</st>!<n id=\"3\" /> ",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> will <st data-num=\"03541 03541 03254\">severely</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">judge</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">if</st> I do not <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">do</st> for David <st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">exactly</st> <st data-num=\"03588 0834\">what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">promised</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">him</st>,<n id=\"2\" />",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "namely, to <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">transfer</st> the <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdom</st> from the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> and to <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">establish</st> the <st data-num=\"03678\" class=\"\">throne</st> of <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> and <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> all the way from <st data-num=\"01835\" class=\"\">Dan</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"0884\" class=\"\">Beer Sheba</st>!\u201d ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "Ish Bosheth<n id=\"1\" /> was <st data-num=\"03808 03201\">unable</st> to <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">answer</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> with even a <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">single</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">word</st> because he was <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">afraid</st> of him.</p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> <st data-num=\"04397 08478\">messengers</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st>, \u201cTo <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">whom</st> does the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> belong? <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">Make</st> an <st data-num=\"01285\" class=\"\">agreement</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> me, <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">will do whatever I can</st><n id=\"3\" /> to cause <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> to <st data-num=\"05437\" class=\"\">turn</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> you.\u201d",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "So David <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"2896\" class=\"\">Good</st>! <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">make</st> an <st data-num=\"01285\" class=\"\">agreement</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> you. <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"07592 0559\">ask</st> <st data-num=\"0389\" class=\"\">only</st> <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">one</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">thing</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">from</st> you. You will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> my <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">face</st> <st data-num=\"03588 0518 06440\">unless</st> you <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughter</st> <st data-num=\"04324\" class=\"\">Michal</st> when you <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> to <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">visit</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">me</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">messengers</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"0378\" class=\"\">Ish Bosheth</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">with this demand</st>:<n id=\"1\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">Give</st> me my <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wife</st> <st data-num=\"04324\" class=\"\">Michal</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">whom</st> I <st data-num=\"0781\" class=\"\">acquired</st><n id=\"2\" /> for <st data-num=\"03967\" class=\"\">100</st> <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistine</st> <st data-num=\"06190\" class=\"\">foreskins</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"0378\" class=\"\">Ish Bosheth</st> <st data-num=\"07971 03947\">took</st> her<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">from</st> her <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">husband</st> <st data-num=\"05973 06409\">Paltiel</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"03919\" class=\"\">Laish</st>. ",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "Her <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">husband</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">went</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">along</st> <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">behind</st> her, <st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">weeping</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">all the way</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"0980\" class=\"\">Bahurim</st>. Finally <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> him, \u201c<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Go</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">back</st>!\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> So he <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">returned</st> home.</p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> <st data-num=\"01697 01961 05973 0559\">advised</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"02205\" class=\"\">elders</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"01571 08543 01571 08032\">Previously</st> you <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">were</st> <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">wanting</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> to be your <st data-num=\"04428 05921\">king</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">Act</st> <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st>! <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"0559 0559\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, \u2018By the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> of my <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> I will <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">save</st><n id=\"1\" /> my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">from</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st> and <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">from</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> their <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st>.\u2019\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">Then</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">spoke</st> <st data-num=\"0241\" class=\"\">privately with</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"01144\" class=\"\">Benjaminites</st>. <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">also</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">went</st> to <st data-num=\"02275\" class=\"\">Hebron</st> to <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">inform</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0241\" class=\"\">privately</st><n id=\"2\" /> of <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> and the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">entire</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of <st data-num=\"01144\" class=\"\">Benjamin</st> had <st data-num=\"02896 05869\">agreed to</st>.<n id=\"3\" />",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "When <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st>, <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">accompanied</st> by <st data-num=\"06242\" class=\"\">20</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st>, <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> in <st data-num=\"02275\" class=\"\">Hebron</st>, <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">prepared</st> a <st data-num=\"04960\" class=\"\">banquet</st> for <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> and the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> were <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> him.",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, \u201cLet me <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">leave</st> so that I may <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">go</st> and <st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">gather</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> my <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">lord</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> so that they may <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">make</st> an <st data-num=\"01285\" class=\"\">agreement</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> you. Then you will <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">rule</st> over <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"0183\" class=\"\">desire</st>.\u201d So <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">away</st>, and he <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">left</st> in <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">peace</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Now</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">soldiers</st><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> were <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">coming back</st> from a <st data-num=\"01416\" class=\"\">raid</st>, <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bringing</st> a <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">great deal</st> of <st data-num=\"07998\" class=\"\">plunder</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> them. <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> <st data-num=\"0369\">was no longer</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> in <st data-num=\"02275\" class=\"\">Hebron</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> David<n id=\"2\" /> had <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> him <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">away</st> and he had <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">left</st> in <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">peace</st>. ",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "When <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">army</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> was <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> him <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">arrived</st>, <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> was <st data-num=\"05046 0559\">told</st>: \u201c<st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"05369\" class=\"\">Ner</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>; he <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> him <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">away</st>, and he <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">left</st> in <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">peace</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">went</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> have you <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st>? <st data-num=\"02009 074\">Abner</st><n id=\"1\" /> has <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> you. <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">would</st> you <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">send</st> him <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">away</st>? Now he\u2019s <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">gone</st> on his <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">way</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "You <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"05369\" class=\"\">Ner</st>. <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Surely</st> he <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> here to <st data-num=\"06601\" class=\"\">spy on</st> you and to <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">determine</st> when you <st data-num=\"04161\" class=\"\">leave</st> and when you <st data-num=\"03996\" class=\"\">return</st><n id=\"1\" /> and to <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">discover</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">everything</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> are <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">doing</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"03318 05973\">left</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> and <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">messengers</st> <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">after</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st>. They <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">brought</st> him <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">back</st> from the <st data-num=\"0953\" class=\"\">well</st> of <st data-num=\"05626\" class=\"\">Sirah</st>. (But <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">aware of it</st>.)",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "When <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">returned</st> to <st data-num=\"02275\" class=\"\">Hebron</st>, <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">took</st> him <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">aside</st> <st data-num=\"0413 08432\">at</st> the <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">gate</st> as if to <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">speak</st> <st data-num=\"07987\" class=\"\">privately</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> him. Joab then <st data-num=\"05221 08033\">stabbed</st> him<n id=\"1\" /> in the <st data-num=\"02570\" class=\"\">abdomen</st> and <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">killed</st> him, avenging the shed <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">blood</st> of his <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">brother</st> <st data-num=\"06214\" class=\"\">Asahel</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">later</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> about <st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">this</st>, he <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> and my <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdom</st> are <st data-num=\"05704 05769\">forever</st> <st data-num=\"05355\" class=\"\">innocent</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">before</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of the <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">shed blood</st> of <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"05369\" class=\"\">Ner</st>. ",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "May his blood <st data-num=\"02342\" class=\"\">whirl</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st> of <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">and</st> the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">entire</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of his <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> May the males of <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">never</st> <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">cease to have</st><n id=\"4\" /> someone <st data-num=\"02100 06879\">with a</st> <st data-num=\"02100\" class=\"\">running sore</st> or a <st data-num=\"06879\" class=\"\">skin disease</st> or one who <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">works</st> at the <st data-num=\"06418\" class=\"\">spindle</st><n id=\"5\" /> or one who <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">falls</st> by the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> or one who <st data-num=\"02638\" class=\"\">lacks</st> <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">food</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> and his <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">brother</st> <st data-num=\"052\" class=\"\">Abishai</st> <st data-num=\"02026\" class=\"\">killed</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st>, <st data-num=\"05921 0834\">because</st> he had <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">killed</st> their <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">brother</st> <st data-num=\"06214\" class=\"\">Asahel</st> in <st data-num=\"01391\" class=\"\">Gibeon</st> during the <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">battle</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "30"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">instructed</st> <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> were <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> him, \u201c<st data-num=\"07167\" class=\"\">Tear</st> your <st data-num=\"0899\" class=\"\">clothes</st>. <st data-num=\"02296\" class=\"\">Put on</st> <st data-num=\"08242\" class=\"\">sackcloth</st>. <st data-num=\"05594\" class=\"\">Lament</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st>!\u201d Now <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">followed</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">behind</st> the <st data-num=\"04296\" class=\"\">funeral pallet</st>.<n id=\"2\" />",
    "verse": "31"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "So they <st data-num=\"06912\" class=\"\">buried</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> in <st data-num=\"02275\" class=\"\">Hebron</st>. The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">cried</st> <st data-num=\"05375 06963\">loudly</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">over</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"06913\" class=\"\">grave</st>, and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">wept</st> too.",
    "verse": "32"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"06969\" class=\"\">chanted</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">the following lament</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cShould <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> have <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">died</st> <st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">like</st> a <st data-num=\"05036\" class=\"\">fool</st>? </p>",
    "verse": "33"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hands</st><n id=\"1\" /> were <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0631\" class=\"\">bound</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and your <st data-num=\"07272\" class=\"\">feet</st> were <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05066\" class=\"\">put</st> into <st data-num=\"05178\" class=\"\">irons</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">You <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fell</st> the way one <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">falls</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> <st data-num=\"01121 05766\">criminals</st>.\u201d<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">wept</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> him <st data-num=\"03254\" class=\"\">again</st>.",
    "verse": "34"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "Then <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> and <st data-num=\"01262\" class=\"\">encouraged</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"01262\" class=\"\">to eat</st> <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">food</st> while it was <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">still</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>. But <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">took an oath</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">punish</st> me <st data-num=\"03541 03541 03254\">severely</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03588 0518\">if</st> I <st data-num=\"02938\" class=\"\">taste</st> <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">bread</st> <st data-num=\"0176\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"03972\" class=\"\">anything</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whatsoever</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> the <st data-num=\"08121\" class=\"\">sun</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">sets</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "35"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"05234\" class=\"\">noticed</st> this and it <st data-num=\"03190\" class=\"\">pleased</st> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">them</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> In fact, <st data-num=\"03605 0834\">everything</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">did</st> <st data-num=\"05869 02896\">pleased</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>. ",
    "verse": "36"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">realized</st> on <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> the <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">killing</st> of <st data-num=\"074\" class=\"\">Abner</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"05369\" class=\"\">Ner</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> done at the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king\u2019s</st> instigation.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "37"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> his <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servants</st>, \u201cDo you <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">realize</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> a <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">leader</st><n id=\"1\" /> has <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fallen</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> in <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>? ",
    "verse": "38"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">Today</st> <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> am <st data-num=\"07390\" class=\"\">weak</st>, even though I am <st data-num=\"04886\" class=\"\">anointed</st> as <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>. <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">These</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> of <st data-num=\"06870\" class=\"\">Zeruiah</st>, are <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">too</st> <st data-num=\"07186\" class=\"\">much</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">for</st> me <st data-num=\"07186\" class=\"\">to bear</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> May the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07999\" class=\"\">punish</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">appropriately</st> the one who has <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st> this <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil thing</st>!\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "39"
  }
]